      <title>CRH 考虑再次尝试出售菲律宾水泥业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/crh-weighs-fresh-sale-attempt-for-philippines-cement-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国-爱尔兰建筑材料集团 CRH Plc 正在考虑重启出售其菲律宾水泥业务。]]></description>
